text: Thank you so much for the e introduction, really appreciate it. I am composing my letter to Karen.

Our school programme is to complete a work experience placement. Not all schools do this in England. Volunteering is completely off your own back. If I get to do my Duke of Edinburgh award (my school still haven't found a coordinator for us) I will be volunteering at the gymnastics club I go to.
I admire your volunteering, I don't know anyone my age that does that volume of volunteering. I definitely think it helps with growing skills and meeting new people.
